search::buildQuery()

Description
    private string search::buildQuery(void)
    Builds a valid MySQL query according to the values class variables contain, such as $this->orderBy or $this->query['where'].

Return Values
    Returns a string containing a valid MySQL query.

Examples
    <?php
	...
	public function getSearchResults() {
	    $qs = $this->buildQueryString();
	    return($this->getRemoteXML($this->URL."?".$qs.";debug=xml"));
	}
	...
    ?>

See Also
    search::buildWhereClause()
    search::createQuery()
